 Microsoft has released MUI (Multilingual User Interface) language packs for Windows

 8.1, Windows 8 and Windows 7. These language packs allow you to apply a new display

 language for your OS. While all of them are available through Windows Update or via

 the Language Control Panel in Windows 8, you might be interested in downloading the

 language pack you use permanently to your hard drive, e.g. to install it on

 multiple PCs at once, or if you don't want to download the huge files all over
